Description: STRATOCASTER STYLE DOUBLE FAT . I PUT THIS GUITAR TOGETHER MYSELF WITH TWO AFTER MARKET HUMBUCKERS WIRED ON 3 WAY SWITCH. PICK GUARD HAS SOME SCRATCHES . A CHANCE TO GET A DOUBLE HUMBUCKER FOR LOW MONEY. WEIGHT ABOUT 6-1/2 lbs on BATH SCALE. SORRY MY DIGITAL POSTAL SCALE WENT ON THE FRITZ ALL OF A SUDDEN.
Title: STRATOCASTER DOUBLE FAT SUNBURST FINISH WITH ROSEWOOD NECK
